 <span data-ttu-id="f6007-212">다음 예제에서는 정의 대 한 정보를 수집 하는 이벤트 처리기는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> 이벤트입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f6007-212">The following example defines an event handler that gathers information about an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> event.</span></span>  
  
